        {
            "title": "商米科技暗盤中段較招股價高約2.7倍 股份明首掛",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">商米科技(06810)股份將於明天掛牌，今午暗盤中段已較招股價高約2.7倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"商米科技招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/06810.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"商米科技招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/06810.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">商米科技招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至下午約5時44分，輝立交易平台顯示商米的暗盤約為92.8元，較招股價高2.73倍；富途交易平台顯示的暗盤價也達92.1元，比招股價高2.7倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15933374-%e5%95%86%e7%b1%b3%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e8%bc%83%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e9%ab%98%e7%b4%842-7%e5%80%8d-%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e6%98%8e%e9%a6%96%e6%8e%9b",
